==Area and boundaries==
'''Area:'''
<br />''total:''
110,910&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup>
<br />''land:''
110,550&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup>
<br />''water:''
360&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup>

'''Area - comparative:'''
slightly larger than [[Tennessee]], about 20% of the total area of [[France]].

'''Land boundaries:'''
<br />''total:''
1,808&nbsp;km
<br />''border countries:''
[[Greece]] 494&nbsp;km, The [[Republic of Macedonia]] 148&nbsp;km, [[Romania]] 608&nbsp;km, [[Serbia]] 318&nbsp;km, [[Turkey]] 240&nbsp;km

'''Coastline:'''
354&nbsp;km

