==Resources and land use==
'''Natural resources:'''
[[bauxite]], [[copper]], [[lead]], [[zinc]], [[uranium]], [[bismuth]], [[nickel]], [[coal]], [[timber]], arable land

'''Land use:'''
<br />''arable land:''
43%
<br />''permanent crops:''
2%
<br />''permanent pastures:''
14%
<br />''forests and woodland:''
38%
<br />''other:''
3% (1999 est.)

'''Irrigated land:'''
12,370&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> (1993 est.)

'''Geography - note:'''
strategic location near [[Turkish Straits]]; controls key land routes from Europe to Asia

